      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay. i think i'll do that. i'm a bit worried though because my left arm feels kinda heavy and tingly too, but i probably just slept on it wrong or something? i feel like i'm just really overheated. you think i can just wait an hour or two and see if the coconut water helps before i worry about anything else?",
