      "role": "user",
      "content": "yea i think i'll just try the shower and some more coconut water first. i really dont want to go to the hospital if i dont have to, it's such a hassle and i'm mostly fine except for the talking thing. if i just drink a lot of electrolytes and lay down in a cool room for a bit, that'll definitely clear it up right? it's basically just my body reacting to the heat, so once i'm hydrated i should be back to normal in a few hours?",
